title: C08W 4G GPS Tracker
metaDesc: High-precision C08W 4G GPS tracking device offering real-time location monitoring and advanced fleet analytics.
fullDescription: Compact ultra-thin IP65 waterproof design, integrating high-sensitivity GPS/BeiDou/LBS positioning for real-time tracking. Features ACC detection, intelligent alarms (fence/speed/power), and a robust watchdog system for system stability. Ideal for car rental, logistics, private cars, and electric scooters.
features: Compact & Waterproof: 14mm thick ultra-thin design with IP65 rating
Intelligent Alerts: Fence entry/exit, speeding, power outage, and vibration alarms
Robust Stability: Built-in watchdog functionality with auto-recovery from crashes
Versatile Application: Suitable for 9-90V vehicles including logistics trucks, rental cars, and scooters
packaging: 1x C08W Unit, 1x Power Cable, 1x User Manual, 1x Relay (Optional)
